author: Huawei
description:
#Huawei #DigitALLNight2025 drew more than 1,000 students in Madrid and more than 300 in eight other venues around Europe where they explored Huawei's latest technical innovations and valuable career opportunities available to STEM and ICT students.
 
As part of #HUAWEICONNECT, DigitALL Night is an annual flagship talent event designed for students and young professionals to explore Huawei's cutting-edge technologies and learn about the diverse career paths. Ready to kick-start your career at Huawei? Here's your chance. Apply for a graduate position: https://bit.ly/4oZVpg8
title: Huawei DigitALL Night 2025: Cultivating Tech Talent in Europe

author: Huawei
description:
The #Huawei Innovation & Intellectual Property Forum 2025 showcased the power of openness in driving progress, highlighted by Huawei's sixth edition of its Top Ten Inventions. 
 
The Top Ten Inventions include breakthroughs in computing, AI acceleration, next-generation operating systems, advanced connectivity, green networks, innovative device design, and assisted driving technologies. Watch the highlights to discover the latest tech innovations, and learn more about #IPR2025, "Advancing Innovation with Openness": https://bit.ly/47P0RLU #IPMatters
title: Huawei's 2025 Top Ten Inventions Power the Next Wave of Technology
